Technically, we focus on the BERT language model [bert], and the Wikidata knowledge base. Although BERT has been superseded by newer LMs, its popularity is still matched only by the closed source GPT-3 and chatGPT models. Wikidata is by far the most prominent and comprehensive public KB, so evaluations against it provide the strongest yardstick.